{"tid":1645550,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"13歲女童被捕後住女童院27日後無被起訴","createTime":"2019-10-11T02:32:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-11T12:08:43.000Z","uid":56881,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"7cbeb5f5609f0481134760c517c8708e1034aa75","tid":1645550,"uid":56881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T02:32:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/13%E6%AD%B2%E5%A5%B3%E7%AB%A5%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95%E5%BE%8C%E4%BD%8F%E5%A5%B3%E7%AB%A5%E9%99%A227%E6%97%A5%E5%BE%8C%E7%84%A1%E8%A2%AB%E8%B5%B7%E8%A8%B4-012935995.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F13%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E7%25AB%25A5%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258D%2595%25E5%25BE%258C%25E4%25BD%258F%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E7%25AB%25A5%25E9%2599%25A227%25E6%2597%25A5%25E5%25BE%258C%25E7%2584%25A1%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E8%25B5%25B7%25E8%25A8%25B4-012935995.html&d=tgdX0zC4r3YoKKw%2Bq%2FbDqebr9%2BGymSeLOXabm6KdyvY%3D&h=db99b740\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/13%E6%AD%B2%E5%A5%B3%E7%AB%A5%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95%E5%BE%8C%E4%BD%8F%E5%A5%B3%E7%AB%A5%E9%99%A227%E6%97%A5%E5%BE%8C%E7%84%A1%E8%A2%AB%E8%B5%B7%E8%A8%B4-012935995.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/HTm0Ao0HDv8remKvXy6XIg--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MzU5O2g9MjAyO2lsPXBsYW5l/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/News/now.com/TEEN-ARREST-HOLD-191011.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FHTm0Ao0HDv8remKvXy6XIg--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MzU5O2g9MjAyO2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2FNews%2Fnow.com%2FTEEN-ARREST-HOLD-191011.jpg&h=97965a50&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n13歲女童被捕後住女童院27日後無被起訴<br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】六月至今，12至15歲被捕人士累計有104人，其中一名13歲女童在警方申請保護令期間，入住兒童院27日，事後卻無被起訴。有律師質疑警方以申請保護令，阻嚇年輕人示威。<br />\n<br />\n8月29日，十三歲升中二的阿妹在深水埗參與社區放映會後，被警方以非法集結罪拘捕，扣留48小時後警方未有落案起訴她，但質疑她的家庭背景不適合照顧，向法庭申請保護令，要她入住兒童院。<br />\n<br />\n由於法庭要進一步索取報告考慮，她被安排暫住兒童院，直至27日後裁判官拒絕警方申請，阿妹才重獲自由。<br />\n<br />\n在兒童院的日子，阿妹生活受到限制，亦不能隨便與家人聯絡。<br />\n<br />\n13歲的她被困27日，似乎未有改變她的想法。<br />\n<br />\n阿妹同案還有兩名初中生，也一度入兒童院暫住等報告，最後都獲釋、沒被起訴，有份跟進的律師質疑警方有意用透過申請保護令，阻嚇未滿16歲的示威者。<br />\n<br />\n根據警方數字，自六月九日至八月二十七日，16歲以下被捕人士有15名，但開學後至九月尾上升至53名，兩星期後至十月十日，人數大幅上升至104人，義務律師接觸不少初中生被捕的個案。<br />\n<br />\n律師又指，他們有責任保障當事人在法律上最大的利益，會提醒16歲以下被捕人士，他們自己可以行使緘默權。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />害人地既仔女"},{"pid":"cc187df3c38115eae0bdb91be4b6ba9108084946","tid":1645550,"uid":256783,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T02:34:19.000Z","msg":"加油 小妹妹<br />\n<br />\n經歷會令你加速成長<br />\n好好記住依段慘痛經歷<br />\n化為力量,  為將來既香港(如有) 發聲<br />\n<br />\n多謝小妹妹"},{"pid":"2d84fac157fa34aa730ea7061b48f1505eb154be","tid":1645550,"uid":264128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T02:35:22.000Z","msg":"對抗警暴，1011 十八區開花<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1644865\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1644865</a>"},{"pid":"99b044b3b797a17b3e5575196309564e546077fa","tid":1645550,"uid":38109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T02:39:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6af7732a4ee460a28900b1e850f7859f845d0258","tid":1645550,"uid":127067,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T11:48:18.000Z","msg":"今日原來係國際女童日，twitter戰線請起動 #dayofthegirl"},{"pid":"526ef190c4fcb6812db17c563b5a04f38d37b704","tid":1645550,"uid":279497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T12:08:43.000Z","msg":"推"}]}